#. module: summer_camps
#: model_terms:event.event,ticket_instructions:summer_camps.event_event_1
#: model_terms:event.event,ticket_instructions:summer_camps.event_event_2
#: model_terms:event.event,ticket_instructions:summer_camps.event_event_3
#: model_terms:event.event,ticket_instructions:summer_camps.event_event_4
#: model_terms:event.type,ticket_instructions:summer_camps.event_type_1
msgid ""
"Take a train to <strong>Marloie Station</strong>. From there, we offer a "
"supervised shuttle service to camp for an extra fee. Don’t forget to book it "
"in advance through your dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Tag et tog til <strong>Marloie Station</strong>. Derfra tilbyder vi en "
"overvåget shuttle-service til lejren mod et ekstra gebyr. Glem ikke at booke "
"den på forhånd via dit dashboard."

#. module: summer_camps
#: model:project.project,label_tasks:summer_camps.project_project_1
msgid "Tasks"
msgstr "Opgaver"

#. module: summer_camps
#: model_terms:event.event,ticket_instructions:summer_camps.event_event_1
#: model_terms:event.event,ticket_instructions:summer_camps.event_event_2
#: model_terms:event.event,ticket_instructions:summer_camps.event_event_4
#: model_terms:event.type,ticket_instructions:summer_camps.event_type_1
msgid ""
"Thank you for booking your child’s place at <strong>Camp Adventure</strong>! "
"We’re thrilled to welcome them to an unforgettable summer in the heart of "
"the Ardennes."
msgstr ""
"Tak, fordi du har reserveret en plads til dit barn på <strong>Camp "
"Adventure</strong>! Vi glæder os til at byde dem velkommen til en "
"uforglemmelig sommer i hjertet af Ardennerne."

#. module: summer_camps
#: model_terms:event.event,ticket_instructions:summer_camps.event_event_3
msgid ""
"Thank you for booking your child’s place at <strong>Camp Arts</strong>! "
"We’re thrilled to welcome them to an unforgettable summer in the heart of "
"the Ardennes."
msgstr ""
"Tak, fordi du har reserveret en plads til dit barn på <strong>Camp Arts</"
"strong>! Vi glæder os til at byde dem velkommen til en uforglemmelig sommer "
"i hjertet af Ardennerne."

#. module: summer_camps
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:summer_camps.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The <strong>Appointments</strong> app makes it easy for families to connect "
"with your team before committing to a camp. Whether they want to ask "
"questions, discuss special needs, or find the best fit for their child, this "
"tool helps you offer personalized service—without the back-and-forth of "
"scheduling emails."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Aftalerappen</strong> gør det nemt for familier at komme i kontakt "
"med dit team, inden de tilmelder sig et lejr. Uanset om de ønsker at stille "
"spørgsmål, drøfte særlige behov eller finde det bedste tilbud til deres "
"barn, hjælper dette værktøj dig med at tilbyde personlig service – uden frem "
"og tilbage med e-mails om planlægning."

#. module: summer_camps
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:summer_camps.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The <strong>CRM</strong> app helps you manage every inquiry that comes "
"through your website's contact form—turning initial interest into confirmed "
"registrations. Whether it's a parent asking for more info, a school "
"proposing a group booking, or a returning family inquiring about "
"availability, the CRM keeps your sales pipeline organized and actionable."
msgstr ""
"<strong>CRM-appen</strong> hjælper dig med at administrere alle "
"henvendelser, der kommer ind via din hjemmesides kontaktformular, og "
"omdanner den indledende interesse til bekræftede tilmeldinger. Uanset om det "
"er en forælder, der beder om mere information, en skole, der foreslår en "
"gruppebestilling, eller en tilbagevendende familie, der spørger om ledige "
"pladser, holder CRM-systemet din salgspipeline organiseret og klar til "
"handling."

#. module: summer_camps
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:summer_camps.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The <strong>Events</strong> app is the heart of summer camp management. It "
"provides tools to create, customize, and manage all aspects of each camp "
"session."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Arrangementerappen</strong> spiller en central rolle i "
"administrationen af sommerlejrene. Den indeholder værktøjer til at oprette, "
"tilpasse og administrere alle aspekter af hver lejr."

#. module: summer_camps
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:summer_camps.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The <strong>Projects</strong> app helps with behind-the-scenes preparation "
"and operational planning."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Projekterappen</strong> hjælper med forberedelser bag kulisserne og "
"driftsplanlægning."

#. module: summer_camps
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:summer_camps.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The <strong>Sign</strong> app allows you to collect parental authorizations "
"quickly and securely through digital signatures. It's a reliable way to "
"ensure compliance while minimizing paperwork."
msgstr ""
"<strong>E-Signaturappen</strong> giver dig mulighed for hurtigt og sikkert "
"at indsamle forældresamtykker via digitale e-signaturer. Det er en pålidelig "
"måde at sikre overholdelse af reglerne på, samtidig med at papirarbejdet "
"minimeres."

#. module: summer_camps
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:summer_camps.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The <strong>Website</strong> app allows you to showcase your summer camps in "
"a visually appealing and informative way. It serves as the entry point for "
"parents and guardians to discover camp offerings, explore details, and "
"register children directly online."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Hjemmesideappen</strong> giver dig mulighed for at præsentere dine "
"sommerlejre på en visuelt tiltalende og informativ måde. Den fungerer som "
"indgang for forældre og værger, der ønsker at se lejrtilbud, udforske "
"detaljer og tilmelde børn direkte online."

#. module: summer_camps
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:summer_camps.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The bottom of the Email template contains an \"Attachments\" section. Here, "
"you can add files to send automatically with the template, such as a packing "
"list, more information, etc."
msgstr ""
"Nederst i e-mailskabelonen er der et afsnit med \"Vedhæftede filer\". Her "
"kan du tilføje filer, der automatisk sendes sammen med skabelonen, f.eks. en "
"pakkeliste, yderligere oplysninger osv."

#. module: summer_camps
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:summer_camps.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The result? Better service, more trust, and a smoother registration journey."
msgstr ""
"Resultatet? Bedre service, større tillid og en mere smidig "
"registreringsproces."

#. module: summer_camps
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:summer_camps.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"These are defined in the questions. To associate a product to a response, "
"set the question type to \"<strong>Selection</strong>\". Following that, set "
"a new or existing product in the \"Event Product\" column."
msgstr ""

#. module: summer_camps
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:summer_camps.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"These should now both appear during the payment process, and in the Sales "
"Order that's associated to the attendee registration."
msgstr ""

