#: model:project.task.type,name:summer_camps.project_task_type_1
msgid "To do"
msgstr "Gøremål"

#. module: summer_camps
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:summer_camps.welcome_article_body
msgid "Track real-time performance via the <strong>Events dashboard</strong>."
msgstr ""
"Følg resultaterne i realtid via <strong>Arrangementerdashboardet</strong>."

#. module: summer_camps
#: model_terms:event.event,description:summer_camps.event_event_1
#: model_terms:event.event,description:summer_camps.event_event_2
#: model_terms:event.event,description:summer_camps.event_event_3
#: model_terms:event.event,description:summer_camps.event_event_4
msgid "Transport to/from the camp (optional shuttle service available)"
msgstr "Transport til/fra lejren (valgfri shuttle-service tilgængelig)"

#. module: summer_camps
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:summer_camps.ir_ui_view_916
msgid "Trust us with your children and enjoy your summer with peace of mind"
msgstr "Overlad dine børn til os, og nyd sommeren med ro i sindet"

#. module: summer_camps
#: model_terms:product.public.category,website_description:summer_camps.product_public_category_2
msgid "Unleash creativity with supplies for unforgettable projects."
msgstr "Slip kreativiteten løs med materialer til uforglemmelige projekter."

#. module: summer_camps
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:summer_camps.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use <strong>event templates</strong> for recurring camp formats to save time."
msgstr ""
"Brug <strong>arrangementerskabeloner</strong> til tilbagevendende "
"lejrformater for at spare tid."

#. module: summer_camps
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:summer_camps.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use <strong>tags</strong> to categorize camps by duration, activities, "
"lodging type, or meal plans."
msgstr ""
"Brug <strong>tags</strong> til at kategorisere lejre efter varighed, "
"aktiviteter, indkvarteringstype eller måltidsplaner."

#. module: summer_camps
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:summer_camps.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use the <strong>Registration Desk view</strong> to check campers in upon "
"arrival."
msgstr ""
"Brug visningen <strong>Tilmeldingsskranke</strong> til at tjekke "
"lejrdeltagere ind ved ankomsten."

#. module: summer_camps
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:summer_camps.ir_ui_view_916
msgid ""
"We focus on confidence-building, creativity, nature immersion, and friendship"
"—all in a safe, supervised, and joy-filled environment."
msgstr ""
"Vi fokuserer på selvtillid, kreativitet, naturforbindelse og venskab – alt "
"sammen i et sikkert, overvåget og glædesfyldt miljø."

#. module: summer_camps
#: model_terms:event.event,description:summer_camps.event_event_1
#: model_terms:event.event,description:summer_camps.event_event_2
#: model_terms:event.event,description:summer_camps.event_event_3
#: model_terms:event.event,description:summer_camps.event_event_4
msgid ""
"We handle allergies and medical needs with great care—just note everything "
"during registration. Our staff is first-aid certified and always nearby."
msgstr ""
"Vi håndterer allergier og medicinske behov med stor omhu – bare notér alt "
"under tilmeldingen. Vores personale er førstehjælpscertificeret og altid i "
"nærheden."

#. module: summer_camps
#: model_terms:event.event,description:summer_camps.event_event_1
#: model_terms:event.event,description:summer_camps.event_event_2
#: model_terms:event.event,description:summer_camps.event_event_3
#: model_terms:event.event,description:summer_camps.event_event_4
msgid "Welcome kit with water bottle, badge &amp; field journal"
msgstr "Velkomstpakke med vandflaske, badge og feltdagbog"

#. module: summer_camps
#: model_terms:event.event,description:summer_camps.event_event_1
#: model_terms:event.event,description:summer_camps.event_event_4
msgid ""
"Welcome to <strong>Adventure Summer Camp </strong>—where kids unplug from "
"screens and reconnect with nature, challenge themselves, and build "
"friendships that last a lifetime. Set in the heart of the <strong>Belgian "
"Ardennes</strong>, our adventure camp is all about movement, teamwork, and "
"muddy boots. Every day brings a new thrill—from forest games to climbing and "
"campfire stories.<br><br>"
msgstr ""
"Velkommen til <strong>Adventure Summer Camp </strong>—hvor børnene kobler af "
"fra skærmene og genfinder kontakten med naturen, udfordrer sig selv og "
"knytter venskaber, der varer hele livet. Beliggende i hjertet af <STRONG>de "
"belgiske Ardenner</STRONG> handler vores eventyrlejr om bevægelse, teamwork "
"og mudrede støvler. Hver dag byder på nye spændende oplevelser—fra skovlege "
"til klatring og historier ved lejrbålet.<BR><BR>"

#. module: summer_camps
#: model_terms:event.event,description:summer_camps.event_event_3
msgid ""
"Welcome to <strong>Art &amp; Creative Camp</strong> at Camp Sylva—a week-"
"long adventure into color, creativity, and self-expression. Set in the "
"peaceful forests of the Belgian Ardennes, this camp is designed for curious "
"minds and messy hands. Campers dive into a wide range of artistic "
"disciplines in a playful, encouraging environment that celebrates "
"individuality."
msgstr ""
"Velkommen til <strong>Kunst &amp; Creative Camp</strong> på Camp Sylva – et "
"ugelangt eventyr i farver, kreativitet og selvudfoldelse. Beliggende i de "
"fredelige skove i de belgiske Ardenner er dette camp designet til nysgerrige "
"sind og kreative hænder. Deltagerne dykker ned i en bred vifte af "
"kunstneriske discipliner i et legende og opmuntrende miljø, der hylder "
"individualitet."

#. module: summer_camps
#: model_terms:event.event,description:summer_camps.event_event_2
msgid ""
"Welcome to IT Summer Camp at Camp Sylva—a unique tech adventure for curious "
"minds ready to dive into the world of programming, robotics, and digital "
"creativity. Surrounded by nature but powered by innovation, campers will "
"spend the week learning essential coding skills, tackling team challenges, "
"and discovering the magic of building things that work."
msgstr ""
"Velkommen til IT-sommerlejren på Camp Sylva – et unikt teknologisk eventyr "
"for nysgerrige sjæle, der er klar til at dykke ned i programmering, "
"robotteknologi og digital kreativitet. Omgivet af natur og drevet af "
"innovation vil deltagerne i løbet af en uge opbygge vigtige "
"programmeringsfærdigheder, løse udfordringer i teams og opleve glæden ved at "
"skabe ting, der virker."

#. module: summer_camps
#: model_terms:appointment.type,message_intro:summer_camps.appointment_type_1
msgid ""
"Whether you're wondering about daily activities, camper safety, food "
"options, or what to pack—we're here to help."
msgstr ""
"Uanset om du har spørgsmål om daglige aktiviteter, sikkerhed for deltagerne, "
"madmuligheder eller hvad du skal pakke – så er vi her for at hjælpe."

#. module: summer_camps
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:summer_camps.ir_ui_view_916
msgid "Why Choose Our Camps?"
msgstr "Hvorfor vælge vores lejre?"

#. module: summer_camps
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:summer_camps.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"With Odoo CRM, you stay on top of every conversation and never let a "
"potential camper slip through the cracks."
msgstr ""
"Med Odoo CRM har du styr på alle samtaler og lader aldrig en potentiel "
"deltager slippe gennem fingrene."

#. module: summer_camps
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:summer_camps.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"With Odoo, managing your summer camp becomes easier, more professional, and "
"better connected. Ready to take your camp operations to the next level? "
"Let’s build something great together."
msgstr ""
"Med Odoo bliver administrationen af dine sommerlejre nemmere, mere "
"professionel og bedre forbundet. Er du klar til at tage driften af dine "
"lejre til det næste niveau? Lad os skabe noget fantastisk sammen."

#. module: summer_camps
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:summer_camps.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"With just a few clicks, parents can book a call or in-person meeting "
"directly from your website or email campaigns. You and your colleagues stay "
"organized, avoid double-bookings, and ensure every camper is matched with "
"the right experience."
msgstr ""
"Med blot et par klik kan forældre booke et opkald eller et personligt møde "
"direkte via jeres hjemmeside eller e-mailkampagner. I og jeres kolleger kan "
"nemt holde overblikket, undgå dobbeltbookinger og sikre, at alle deltagere "
"får den rette oplevelse."

#. module: summer_camps
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:summer_camps.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Would you like to discuss your Odoo setup with us or explore more features?"
msgstr ""
"Vil du gerne tale med os om dit Odoo-setup eller drøfte nogle spørgsmål mere "
"detaljeret?"

#. module: summer_camps
#: model_terms:event.event,description:summer_camps.event_event_1
#: model_terms:event.event,description:summer_camps.event_event_2
#: model_terms:event.event,description:summer_camps.event_event_3
#: model_terms:event.event,description:summer_camps.event_event_4
msgid ""
"Yes. All activities are supervised, age-appropriate, and use certified "
"safety gear. We never push kids beyond their comfort zones."
msgstr ""
"Ja. Alle aktiviteter foregår under opsyn, er alderssvarende, og der anvendes "
"certificeret sikkerhedsudstyr. Vi overbelaster aldrig børnene."

#. module: summer_camps
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:summer_camps.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can also export all answers in bulk in a template by opening the "
"template, then clicking the gear icon, then \"Export Answers\"."
msgstr ""

#. module: summer_camps
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:summer_camps.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can easily edit your email templates. Enter \"/\" to access special "
"styling features, such as buttons, tables, bold, italics, links, and so on."
msgstr ""
"Du kan nemt redigere dine e-mailskabeloner. Indtast \"/\" for at få adgang "
"til formateringsfunktioner som knapper, tabeller, fed skrift, kursiv, links "
"osv."

#. module: summer_camps
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:summer_camps.welcome_article_body
msgid "You can still do it by upgrading your package in Apps."
msgstr "Du kan fortsat gøre dette ved at opdatere din pakke via Apps."

#. module: summer_camps
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:summer_camps.ir_ui_view_916
msgid "Your choice of sports between football, basketball and windsurfing"
msgstr "Du kan vælge mellem sportsgrenene fodbold, basketball og windsurfing"

#. module: summer_camps
#: model_terms:event.event,ticket_instructions:summer_camps.event_event_1
